				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Imbued Rubies are basically Rubies imbued by Clerics. The Everhot who tells you about the Brellium weapons says something about the Cleric of Underfoot(the Kaladim Cleric Guild) being able to imbue them if you are on good terms with them. Not sure if this means they will imbue it if you give it to them, or if you should hail out a Cleric(PC) to imbue it, but that's what Imbued Rubies are.<BR>
